about.title: Hi Iam Emanuel Funes
about.aboutMe: I am a Full Stack Web developer, I master technologies such as React and Next.js for the Frontend, and Express, SQL and MongoDB for the Backend. I stand out for my speed in learning new technologies, efficiency in solving problems and ability to collaborate in teams. I am looking for new challenges to continue growing professionally and contribute to the success of dynamic and innovative technology projects. Translated with DeepL.com (free version)

experienceOne.title: Frontend React Developer
experienceOne.description: Participated in the development of a sports betting web application, implementing responsive user interfaces based on pre-established designs and developing REST API integrations. Worked with modern technologies including React, TypeScript, Vite, and CSS to create reusable components and optimize user experience.

experienceTwo.title: Full Stack Developer
experienceTwo.description: Contributed to the development of an AI agents web platform, covering both backend and frontend development. Implemented end-to-end functionalities using Next.js, Express.js, Chakra UI, Tailwind CSS, TypeScript, KNEX ORM, and MySQL, focusing on scalable architecture and AI services integration.

experienceThree.title: Freelance Full Stack Developer
experienceThree.description: Participated in multiple freelance projects developing and maintaining full stack web functionalities. Implemented new features and improvements in both frontend and backend, using the following technologies: Next.js, ShadCN/UI, TypeScript, TanStack, Nest.js, MongoDB, Prisma, and Strapi.
